data. Start your journey to experience management and try a free account today.","SurveyName":"Receiver_Randomized","ProtectSelectionIds":true}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1","SecondaryAttribute":"Please read the following self-introduction from Priya Nair: \u00a0 Priya Nair, 44, Singapore-based su..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please read the following self-introduction from <b>Priya Nair<\/b>:<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Priya Nair, 44, Singapore-based supply chain executive at Luminos Tech. Grew up in Chennai, studied in Mumbai, got her master's at NUS. Fifteen years in the industry, starting in procurement before getting pulled into logistics and never looking back. Travels constantly between Taipei, Rotterdam, and Mexico City.<\/div><div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><br><\/div><div style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Colleagues describe Priya as thoughtful and fair, someone who follows through on commitments and takes responsibility for shared outcomes. She believes that trust is built through consistency and mutual respect, especially when working with people from different backgrounds.<br>\n<br>\nOutside work she runs half marathons, rewatches crime dramas, and tends a small herb garden on her balcony with surprising dedication.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID1","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please read the following self-introduction from Priya Nair: \u00a0 Priya Nair, 44, Singapore-based su...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID2","SecondaryAttribute":"You perceived the trust relationship between you and\u00a0Priya Nair\u00a0as","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"You perceived the trust relationship between you and&nbsp;<strong>Priya Nair<\/strong>&nbsp;as","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You perceived the trust relationship between you and\u00a0Priya Nair\u00a0as","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Totally stranger"},"2":{"Display":"Have some thin trust (i.e., Have some information about her)"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID2"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID3","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that Priya Nair wrote. Their...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that <strong>Priya Nair<\/strong> wrote.<br>\n<u>Their company actively encourages the use of AI to draft, refine, and optimize the content.<\/u><\/h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><strong>Strategic Recommendations<\/strong><br>\nTo insulate the organization from future shocks, we must execute the following three strategies:<\/p>\n\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Regionalized Hubs (Near-shoring): Shift 30% of production to facilities within the same hemisphere as our primary consumer base. This reduces shipping costs and slashes transit-related emissions.<\/li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Predictive Inventory Buffer: Move away from lean \"Just-in-Time\" models to a strategic buffer system for \"Class A\" components, ensuring 99% availability even during transit disruptions.<\/li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Circular Material Integration: Implement a \"Take-Back\" program where 20% of raw materials for new products are harvested from recycled end-of-life units.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><strong>Risk-Benefit Analysis<\/strong><br>\nThe primary hurdle is a 6% increase in unit production costs due to higher labor rates in near-shored regions. However, this is offset by the reduction in emergency air-freight costs and brand equity gains.<br>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><em>AI-disclosure: The executive summary was created with assistance from Gemini 3 and has been reviewed and edited by a human.<\/em><\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that Priya Nair wrote. Their...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID3"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID4","SecondaryAttribute":"In terms of AI-use in working environment, Priya Nair's company...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In terms of AI-use in working environment, <b>Priya Nair's company<\/b>...","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In terms of AI-use in working environment, Priya Nair's company...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"acknowledges the use of AI as a standard tool for content drafting"},"2":{"Display":"actively encourages the use of AI to draft, refine, and optimize the content"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID4"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID5","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Re...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.<br><br>Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. <br><br>Priya can transfer X dollar to you, where X is an integer and 0 \u2264 X \u2264 3.&nbsp;The amount Priya transfers to you will be <u>tripled<\/u>, so you receives <u>3X<\/u> units.<br><br>Now you decide the amount Y transferring back to Priya, where 0 \u2264 Y \u2264 3X. Please enter the amount you would like to send back in different scenarios below.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionType":"CS","Selector":"VR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":9},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Re...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Priya transferred $0 to you (you can only enter 0)"},"2":{"Display":"Priya transferred $1 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 3)"},"3":{"Display":"Priya transferred $2 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 6)"},"4":{"Display":"Priya transferred $3 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 9)"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4],"Validation":{"Settings":{"EnforceRange":"ON","Type":"None","ForceResponse":"OFF","ChoiceTotal":"100","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $0 (you can only enter 0)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 0 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID5","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"0","Type":"Expression"},"1":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/2","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $1 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 3)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Less Than or Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 3 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/2","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"LessThanOrEqual","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID5","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"3","Type":"Expression"},"2":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/3","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $2 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 6)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 6 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/3","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID5","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"6","Type":"Expression"},"3":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/4","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $3 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 9)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 9 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID5\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/4","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID5","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID5","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"9","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"Require valid number","libraryID":null,"messageID":null,"subMessageID":"VE_VALIDNUMBER"}}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":6,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"Click to write Label 1"},"2":{"Display":"Click to write Label 2"},"3":{"Display":"Click to write Label 3"}},"ClarifyingSymbolType":"None"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID6","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that Priya Nair wrote. Their...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that <strong>Priya Nair<\/strong> wrote.<br>\n<u>Their company acknowledges the use of AI as a standard tool for content drafting.<\/u><\/h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><strong>Strategic Recommendations<\/strong><br>\nTo insulate the organization from future shocks, we must execute the following three strategies:<\/p>\n\n<ul dir=\"ltr\">\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Regionalized Hubs (Near-shoring): Shift 30% of production to facilities within the same hemisphere as our primary consumer base. This reduces shipping costs and slashes transit-related emissions.<\/li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Predictive Inventory Buffer: Move away from lean \"Just-in-Time\" models to a strategic buffer system for \"Class A\" components, ensuring 99% availability even during transit disruptions.<\/li>\n\t<li style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">Circular Material Integration: Implement a \"Take-Back\" program where 20% of raw materials for new products are harvested from recycled end-of-life units.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><strong>Risk-Benefit Analysis<\/strong><br>\nThe primary hurdle is a 6% increase in unit production costs due to higher labor rates in near-shored regions. However, this is offset by the reduction in emergency air-freight costs and brand equity gains.<\/p>\n\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><br>\n<em>AI-disclosure: The executive summary was created with assistance from Gemini 3 and has been reviewed and edited by a human.<\/em><\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine the following paragraphs being part of the executive summary that Priya Nair wrote. Their...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID6"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID7","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine you are now going to play a game with Priya Nair.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine you are now going to play a game with <b>Priya Nair<\/b>.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID7","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine you are now going to play a game with Priya Nair.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID8","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair again. Priya is the Sender, and you are...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with <b>Priya Nair<\/b> <u>again<\/u>. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.<br><br>Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. <br><br>Priya can transfer X dollar to you, where X is an integer and 0 \u2264 X \u2264 3.&nbsp;The amount Priya transfers to you will be <u>tripled<\/u>, so you receives <u>3X<\/u> units.<br><br>Now you decide the amount Y transferring back to Priya, where 0 \u2264 Y \u2264 3X. Please enter the amount you would like to send back in different scenarios below.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"CS","Selector":"VR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":9},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair again. Priya is the Sender, and you are...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Priya transferred $0 to you (you can only enter 0)"},"2":{"Display":"Priya transferred $1 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 3)"},"3":{"Display":"Priya transferred $2 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 6)"},"4":{"Display":"Priya transferred $3 to you (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 9)"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4],"Validation":{"Settings":{"EnforceRange":"ON","Type":"None","ForceResponse":"OFF","ChoiceTotal":"100","CustomValidation":{"Logic":{"0":{"0":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $0 (you can only enter 0)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Less Than or Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 0 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/1","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"LessThanOrEqual","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID8","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"0","Type":"Expression"},"1":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/2","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $1 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 3)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Less Than or Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 3 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/2","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"LessThanOrEqual","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID8","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"3","Type":"Expression"},"2":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/3","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $2 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 6)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 6 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/3","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID8","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"6","Type":"Expression"},"3":{"ChoiceLocator":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/4","Conjuction":"And","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">And<\/span> <span class=\"QuestionDesc\">Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. Priya can transfer X dollar...<\/span> <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">Priya transferred you $3 (so you can choose an amount between 0 to 9)<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> 9 <\/span>","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/QID8\/ChoiceNumericEntryValue\/4","LogicType":"Question","Operator":"EqualTo","QuestionID":"QID8","QuestionIDFromLocator":"QID8","QuestionIsInLoop":"no","RightOperand":"9","Type":"Expression"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression"},"Message":{"description":"Require valid number","libraryID":null,"messageID":null,"subMessageID":"VE_VALIDNUMBER"}}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":8,"NextAnswerId":6,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"Click to write Label 1"},"2":{"Display":"Click to write Label 2"},"3":{"Display":"Click to write Label 3"}},"ClarifyingSymbolType":"None","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Imagine you are now playing a trust game with Priya Nair. Priya is the Sender, and you are the Recipient.<br><br>Initially, Priya receives an endowment of $3 and you receive $0. <br><br>Priya can transfer X dollar to you, where X is an integer and 0 \u2264 X \u2264 3.&nbsp;The amount Priya transfers to you will be <u>tripled<\/u>, so you receives <u>3X<\/u> units.<br><br>Now you decide the amount Y transferring back to Priya, where 0 \u2264 Y \u2264 3X. Please enter the amount you would like to send back in different scenarios below.<br>","DataExportTag":"","QuestionID":"QID8"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID9","SecondaryAttribute":"Welcome! Thank you for participating in this study. In this survey, you will be asked to imagine...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p>Welcome! Thank you for participating in this study.<\/p>\n\n<p><br \/>\nIn this survey, you will be asked to imagine interacting with another individual in a professional context and to make a series of decisions based on the information provided. Specifically, you will:<br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Get introduced&nbsp;to another person<\/p>\n\t<\/li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Evaluate your perception of your relationship with this person<\/p>\n\t<\/li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Participate in a simple decision-making task involving monetary allocations<\/p>\n\t<\/li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p>Review a short business-related text and answer follow-up questions<\/p>\n\t<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><br \/>\nThe decision-making task you will complete is a commonly used economic game, which will be introduced later.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p><br \/>\nThroughout the survey, please read all materials carefully and answer honestly. Your responses will remain anonymous and will only be used for research purposes.<\/p>\n\n<p><br \/>\nThe survey should take approximately <b>5&ndash;8 minutes<\/b> to complete.<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Welcome! Thank you for participating in this study. In this survey, you will be asked to imagine...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID9"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_9ZWO9LAedszVeho","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":true,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}}]}